data.description: MLS# 271142 Charming historic some newer updates, some newer windows, 4 bedrooms, 2 bath with detached garage-storage space has dirt floor storage area with alley access for all the toys. Basement is Cellar area outside access only.  Large, beautiful home close to downtown Dayton, lots of woodworking, some original wood floors, built-ins to add charm. Master on main level. Has covered porch with garden area or extra parking also. Has lots of storage throughout.  Cellar area with dirt floor is not included in the square footage calculations.  Close to ski area, mountains, wineries, hunting, fishing, and lots of outdoor fun. Call your Realtor or Listing Agent for showings.   LA is related to Seller.
